@startuml
actor AdminOrRecruiter
participant "AuthController" as Controller
participant "AuthServiceImpl" as Service
participant "AdminRepository"
participant "RecruiterRepository"
participant "JwtProvider"
participant "TokenService"

AdminOrRecruiter -> Controller: POST /login (authCode)
Controller -> Service: loginAsAdminOrRecruiter(authCode)

activate Service
Service -> AdminRepository: authCode로 관리자 조회
alt 관리자 존재
    AdminRepository --> Service: User 반환
else 관리자 없음
    Service -> RecruiterRepository: authCode로 채용담당자 조회
    RecruiterRepository --> Service: User 반환 or 예외
end

Service -> JwtProvider: AccessToken 생성
JwtProvider --> Service

Service -> JwtProvider: RefreshToken 생성
JwtProvider --> Service

Service -> TokenService: RefreshToken 저장
note right
authCode가 사용자 식별자(identifier)로 사용됨
RefreshToken은 이 키 기준으로 저장됨
end note

Service --> Controller: AccessToken + RefreshToken 응답
Controller --> AdminOrRecruiter: RefreshToken 쿠키 포함 응답
@enduml
